&lt;p&gt;Jonathan Moch is a Graduate Research Fellow at the Harvard China Project and is pursuing a Ph.D. in Earth and Planetary Sciences with Harvard&amp;#8217;s Atmospheric Chemistry Modeling Group.  Jonathan&amp;#8217;s research interests center on the interactions and feedbacks between climate change and atmospheric chemistry, with a particular focus on China.&lt;/p&gt;
